2015年8月3日，据报道[[弗兰克·格里罗|弗兰克·格里罗]]将在续集中回归出演警长<ref name=GrilloCast>{{cite news|last1=Kroll|first1=Justin|title=Frank Grillo to Return for ‘Purge 3′ (EXCLUSIVE)|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/frank-grillo-purge-3-return-1201555530/|accessdate=2015-08-04|work=variety.com|date=2015-08-03|archive-date=2015-10-20|archive-url=https://archive.today/20151020195800/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/frank-grillo-purge-3-return-1201555530/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月10日，更多演员被公布，其中包括贝蒂·加布里埃尔、艾德文·霍德吉、凯尔·赛科尔、约瑟夫·朱利安·索里亚、麦凯尔泰·威廉逊和伊丽莎白·米歇尔<ref name=Sep2015Deadline>{{cite news|last1=Hipes|first1=Patrick|title=‘Purge 3’ Castings: Universal/Blumhouse Pic Gears Up With Additions|url=http://deadline.com/2015/09/purge-3-cast-mykelti-williamson-elizabeth-mitchell-edwin-hodge-kyle-secor-1201521065/|accessdate=2015-09-10|work=deadline.com|date=2015-09-10|archive-date=2015-10-20|archive-url=https://archive.today/20151020195748/http://deadline.com/2015/09/purge-3-cast-mykelti-williamson-elizabeth-mitchell-edwin-hodge-kyle-secor-1201521065/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

影片于2015年9月16日在[[罗德岛州|罗德岛州]][[文索基特_(罗德岛州)|文索基特]]开拍<ref>{{cite news|title=Filming for 'Purge 3' begins in Woonsocket|url=http://www.valleybreeze.com/2015-09-16/woonsocket-north-smithfield/filming-purge-3-begins-woonsocket#.Vft2S9-qqko|accessdate=2015-09-18|work=valleybreeze.com|date=2015-09-16|archive-date=2015-10-20|archive-url=https://archive.today/20151020195746/http://www.valleybreeze.com/2015-09-16/woonsocket-north-smithfield/filming-purge-3-begins-woonsocket%23.ViacsOLLfK5#.Vft2S9-qqko|dead-url=no}}</ref>。主干道被改造成[[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]]附近的道路<ref>{{cite news|last1=Heim|first1=R.J.|title='Purge 3' begins shooting in Rhode Island|url=http://www.turnto10.com/story/30049210/purge-3-begins-shooting-in-rhode-island|accessdate=2015-09-18|work=turnto10.com|date=2015-09-17|archive-date=2015-10-20|archive-url=https://archive.today/20151020195745/http://turnto10.com/station/news-releases/purge-3-begins-shooting-in-rhode-island|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影片在[[普罗维登斯_(罗德岛州)|普罗维登斯]]杀青<ref>{{cite news|last1=Smith|first1=Andy|title=Movie 'The Purge 3' to film in R.I.|url=http://www.providencejournal.com/article/20150910/NEWS/150919909|accessdate=2015-09-19|work=providencejournal.com|date=2015-09-10|archive-date=2015-10-20|archive-url=https://archive.today/20151020195754/http://www.providencejournal.com/article/20150910/NEWS/150919909|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

