== 迴響 ==
===專業評價===
電影獲得了褒貶不一的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度54%，基於101條評論，平均分為5.4/10<ref name="RT">{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_purge_election_year/ |title=The Purge: Election Year (2016) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2016-06-30 |archive-date=2016-08-28 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20160828230409/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_purge_election_year/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分58<ref name="Meta">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-purge-election-year |title=The Purge: Election Year reviews |website=Metacritic |accessdate=2016-06-30 |archive-date=2016-08-28 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20160828230715/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-purge-election-year |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[IMDB|IMDB]]上得6.5分。評價與前集《[[國定殺戮日：無法無天|國定殺戮日：無法無天]]》相差不遠。

===票房===
在美國和加拿大，該片與《[[吹夢巨人_(2016年電影)|吹夢巨人]]》、《[[泰山傳奇_(電影)|泰山傳奇]]》共同上映競爭，預計能在首映週末獲得約2500萬美元的票房收入<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/bfg-box-office-legend-of-tarzan-1201796977/|title=‘The BFG,’ ‘The Legend of Tarzan’ Failing to Generate Much Box Office Heat|author=Brent Lang|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2016-06-16|accessdate=2016-06-23|archive-date=2016-08-28|archive-url=https://archive.today/20160828225558/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/bfg-box-office-legend-of-tarzan-1201796977/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國首映週末票房為3080萬美元，位居當週票房排名第三，成績優異<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com|title=Box Office Mojo|website=www.boxofficemojo.com|access-date=2016-07-03|archive-date=2016-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160704194902/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

